steps.description:
Write failing test `goto_def_occurrence_param_returns_location` in goto_def.rs::tests — parse 'occurrence def Joint {
    param diameter: Scalar = 10mm
    constraint diameter > 5mm
}', position on 'diameter' in the constraint (line 2, col 15), assert compute_goto_definition returns location pointing to param declaration on line 1. Fails because compute_goto_definition only matches Declaration::Structure.
